Some of the benefits with frequent flyer program include;
Bonus award miles especially to premium Cubin passengers, 
One can upgrade from economy class to business class, 
You can earn free accommodation, 
Access to a high class lounge, 
Increased baggage allowance, 
Reduced ticket fares.


